snippet.title: Darksword: Battle Eternity - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Darksword: Battle Eternity is available now on the Meta Quest Store. Get ready to embark on a dark fantasy adventure, and check out the Darksword: Battle Eternity launch trailer to see some of the fearsome enemies you'll face and more in this VR action RPG.

In Darksword: Battle Eternity, strap on the armor of Blackwolf, a fallen general seeking to free the world from the deadly curse of the Darksword. Develop their own fighting style, exploit enemy weaknesses, and collect materials to craft powerful weapons.
